sed notification laws.</p><p>Not sure whether you have private data? Here are some guidelines. </p>','State Laws',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,0,3,NULL,0,0,'Published',NULL,0.8,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',1,1,NULL,22),(293,24,4,0,1,0,'Page','2008-12-30 18:26:42','2008-12-30 18:38:47','sarbanes-oxley','Sarbanes-Oxley',NULL,'<p class=\"content-header\">Sarbanes-Oxley - Does it Affect me or Not?</p><p>The Sarbanes-Oxley Act (SOX) has caused headaches for many Administrators. Questions abound &ndash; does it apply to IT or doesn&rsquo;t it? If it does, what are the requirements for compliance? Do those products that claim to help with Sarbanes-Oxley compliance actually live up to their marketing claims? Here\'s some information to help you answer those questions for yourself.</p><p>Articles to Answer your Questions:</p><ul><li>Sarbanes-Oxley Act: Security-Relevant or Not?</li><li>COBIT Security</li><li>Best Practices for IT Security &ndash; ISO17799</li></ul><p>Websites:</p><ul><li>The Sarbanes-Oxley Act</li><li>Explanations of the Sarbanes-Oxley Act</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>','Sarbanes-Oxley',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,0,2,NULL,0,0,'Saved (update)',NULL,0.8,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',1,1,NULL,22),(294,24,5,1,1,1,'Page','2008-12-30 18:26:42','2008-12-30 18:38:47','sarbanes-oxley','Sarbanes-Oxley',NULL,'<p class=\"content-header\">Sarbanes-Oxley - Does it Affect me or Not?</p><p>The Sarbanes-Oxley Act (SOX) has caused headaches for many Administrators. Questions abound &ndash; does it apply to IT or doesn&rsquo;t it? If it does, what are the requirements for compliance? Do those products that claim to help with Sarbanes-Oxley compliance actually live up to their marketing claims? Here\'s some information to help you answer those questions for yourself.</p><p>Articles to Answer your Questions:</p><ul><li>Sarbanes-Oxley Act: Security-Relevant or Not?</li><li>COBIT Security</li><li>Best Practices for IT Security &ndash; ISO17799</li></ul><p>Websites:</p><ul><li>The Sarbanes-Ox