p><p>The Companies Act is the United Kingdom\'s version of United States\' Sarbanes-Oxley Act. <a href=\"http://www.opsi.gov.uk/ACTS/acts2004/20040027.htm\" target=\"_blank\">The Act</a>, formally known as the Companies (Audit, Investigations and Community Enterprise) Act, has been passed into law in the UK in response to the Enron fiasco that occurred in the U.S.</p><p>Like SOX, the focus of the Companies Act is to require responsible financial reporting by companies. However, this Act provides considerations for small and medium-sized companies, where SOX makes no such provisions. SOX applies to all publically-traded companies - large or small. And like SOX, the Companies Act contains no specifications for IT Data security; however - just like SOX - it is implied. </p>','The Companies Act',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,0,7,NULL,0,0,'Saved (new)',NULL,0.8,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',1,1,NULL,22),(321,29,3,1,1,1,'Page','2008-12-30 18:51:31','2008-12-30 18:52:29','the-companies-act','The Companies Act',NULL,'<p class=\"content-header\">The Companies Act</p><p>The Companies Act is the United Kingdom\'s version of United States\' Sarbanes-Oxley Act. <a href=\"http://www.opsi.gov.uk/ACTS/acts2004/20040027.htm\" target=\"_blank\">The Act</a>, formally known as the Companies (Audit, Investigations and Community Enterprise) Act, has been passed into law in the UK in response to the Enron fiasco that occurred in the U.S.</p><p>Like SOX, the focus of the Companies Act is to require responsible financial reporting by companies. However, this Act provides considerations for small and medium-sized companies, where SOX makes no such provisions. SOX applies to all publically-traded companies - large or small. And like SOX, the Companies Act contains no specifications for IT Data security; however - just like SOX - it is implied. </p>','The Companies Act',NULL,NULL,NULL,0,1,NULL,0,7,NULL,0,0,'Published',NULL,0.8,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',1,1,NULL,22),(322,22,18,0,1,0,'Page','2008-12-30 15:1